title: 2020 & THE ETHICS OF VOTING - Part 1 Institutions
itunes:author: Toby Buckle
itunes:summary: Ahead of the 2020 presidential election I take on the heated debate on whether leftists should give their support to democrats which whom they may not fully align. I produced an extended analysis of the different issues that are raised in this debate, in this first part I look at political institutions.
